archimate:Principle.name: Data Subject
archimate:Principle.documentation: As defined by the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), any person whose Personal Data is being collected, held, or processed. In the Sovrin Governance Framework, a Data Subject is referred to as an Individual.
